constituent: swift, fishhook, cross, ten, needle, road
heisigStory: Here we see a crossing in the form of a barbed fishhook, suggesting a swifter alternate not only to the roundabouts used in Europe but also to the "cloverleaf" design used on superhighways in the United States.
koohiiStory1: The car went too swiftly through the crossing and was hooked by the cops.
koohiiStory2: In the Heisig version of Frogger, you can image ten giant fish hooks sweeping across the road, with our hapless hero ´froggy´ forced to make a swift crossing or end up as fish bait.
